This is the only pizza oven
factory in the whole city.

00:31:39.690 --> 00:31:41.730
And it still operates
every day.

00:31:41.730 --> 00:31:43.270
They build these pizza ovens.

00:31:43.270 --> 00:31:45.630
So it's still going and
it's still totally

00:31:45.630 --> 00:31:47.470
classic New York thing.

00:31:47.470 --> 00:31:49.760
By the way, this is
on Prince Street.

00:31:49.760 --> 00:31:53.920
If you're ever on Prince and
Bowery, there's two red doors.

00:31:53.920 --> 00:31:56.280
And you can hear them
working on stuff.

00:31:56.280 --> 00:31:57.340
Just open up the doors.

00:31:57.340 --> 00:31:58.430
They're never locked
during the week.

00:31:58.430 --> 00:32:00.870
Just open it, seriously.

00:32:00.870 --> 00:32:01.830
That was when I took
the picture.

00:32:01.830 --> 00:32:04.930
You just open it, and you look
