00:32:15.600 --> 00:32:18.833
And it's really funny to
look in, and people are

00:32:18.833 --> 00:32:19.490
like, wait a second.

00:32:19.490 --> 00:32:22.880
You can go buy a handbag over
here, and you can go buy fancy

00:32:22.880 --> 00:32:24.620
shoes over here, and then there
are these guys working

00:32:24.620 --> 00:32:26.870
on pizza ovens who don't
speak much English.

00:32:26.870 --> 00:32:28.820
These guy's are from
